{"tid":2018753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港話消失同收皮係好可惜 但真心底死","createTime":"2020-05-15T21:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T08:42:13.000Z","uid":203413,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbd958688fa66d0b09eae76c3629f5e78e04c61","tid":2018753,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:05:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3rTLNA8im5k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3rTLNA8im5k&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=3b8211a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3rTLNA8im5k</a><br />\n條片講到香港人成日都話自己地頭既語言好難學。所以比人地第一印象就係難、唔好學、學普通話就夠。<br />\n但講真，你講得到，人地聽得明味得lo，難你條毛咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲鬼佬走去學普通話，開頭都係講野一舊舊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n片中人發音好似我地咩？唔係，但你聽得明。咁味夠lo。想有咩特別技巧呀。<br />\n個個鬼佬講英文都愛爾蘭口音咩？又味係明就夠。<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再阻住地球轉，唔比自己香港文化輸出啦。<br />\n<br />\n啦 醒你地一句<br />\n「真正香港人醒目、姐係智商高係因為佢地既文化。文化根原就係語言、文字。你想唔想學？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8dyrXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8dyrXm.jpg&h=0c6e89e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係自己讚自己呀<br />\n唔咁講點解釋到啲狗咁on9，IQ 咁低，十成個腦送咗中啦，大中華文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後，下次就要識水啲外國人去學香港話啦。"},{"pid":"8948bac57e80898437137a4d21301fafb9f4ef5c","tid":2018753,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:07:47.000Z","msg":"廣東話好難"},{"pid":"b76255e4cbef796782092872ea998a439d508d1b","tid":2018753,"uid":203413,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:07:51.000Z","msg":"唔好負皮先啦 屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ea9fe54d4718d6fe7bba47e5356d56b36cc8c2","tid":2018753,"uid":203413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8948bac57e80898437137a4d21301fafb9f4ef5c","tid":2018753,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:07:47.000Z","msg":"廣東話好難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:08:31.000Z","msg":"做人都好難tim"},{"pid":"6ea2cc4b496e05387c1a88992b1fbfd9fde45bef","tid":2018753,"uid":33770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:09:22.000Z","msg":"底死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c87e2954803c774f61f64310aac216f49aaf061","tid":2018753,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea2cc4b496e05387c1a88992b1fbfd9fde45bef","tid":2018753,"uid":33770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:09:22.000Z","msg":"底死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc2584acdcf55232a60cf3b5bc267213469c8aa","tid":2018753,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051d9419d525338f7bf952bccaec623e8edf970b","tid":2018753,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:33:46.000Z","msg":"sad 無人睇"},{"pid":"8ee22f9cbfdbcbd1a3d0feac81f14d226d55836e","tid":2018753,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T21:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef242cbf536b855dcfaf5707ca12929281e0df0","tid":2018753,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":